# TODO — mcp-proxy

## Phase: 3 (mcp-protocol)

### 3a: JSON-RPC upstream read loop
- [ ] shared/_x: JsonRpcRequest_x, JsonRpcResponse_x types (serde)
- [ ] gateway/_gtw: UpstreamGateway_gtw — BufReader på stdin, læs linje-for-linje, parse JSON-RPC
- [ ] gateway/_gtw: UpstreamWriter_gtw — Mutex<Stdout>, skriv JSON-RPC + newline + flush

### 3b: MCP server (proxy selv)
- [ ] core/_core: McpServer_core — handler for initialize, tools/list, tools/call
- [ ] core/_core: initialize handler — returnér server info + capabilities (tools)
- [ ] core/_core: tools/list handler — returnér proxy-tools + aggregerede downstream tools
- [ ] core/_core: tools/call handler — route til intern handler eller downstream

### 3c: Downstream server registry
- [ ] shared/_x: DownstreamServer_x struct (id, binary, args, child, tools)
- [ ] core/_core: ServerRegistry_core — HashMap<String, DownstreamServer_x>
- [ ] gateway/_gtw: spawn downstream, send initialize, kald tools/list, gem tools
- [ ] gateway/_gtw: send routet tools/call til downstream, læs response

### 3d: Tool routing
- [ ] core/_core: tool namespace — "server-id::tool-name" mapping
- [ ] core/_core: route tools/call — strip prefix, find server, dispatch

### 3e: Proxy management tools
- [ ] core/_core: proxy/load — spawn server, collect tools, list_changed
- [ ] core/_core: proxy/unload — kill server, remove tools, list_changed
- [ ] core/_core: proxy/list — returnér kørende servere

### 3f: list_changed notification
- [ ] adapter/_adp: send notifications/tools/list_changed til upstream efter load/unload

### 3g: Wire + test
- [ ] adapter/_adp: main loop — read upstream → route → respond
- [ ] main.rs: opdater CLI (--config flag valgfri)
- [ ] Verify build: cargo build
- [ ] Test: spawn test-server, verify tools/list aggregering
- [ ] Test: proxy/load + proxy/unload flow

